Pakistan Mari Gas finds major reserve . Mari Gas Company Limited ( MGCL ) said on Monday it had found a major natural gas reserve of probably 1 . 25 trillion cubic feet in Pakistan ' s southern province of Sindh , the official APP news agency said on Monday . APP said MGCL ' s discovery , in Sindh ' s Ghotki district , flowed at a rate of 24 million cubic feet per day . " Based on the completion of this deep well , the tentatively proven gas reserve from the tested intervals is approximately four billion cubic feet and the probable reserves are approximated at 1 . 25 trillion cubic feet , " MGCL said . " It is , therefore , expected to be a substantive discovery of gas in the country . " 
